    // SIGN UP
    br
    .center
      a.waves-effect.waves-light.btn(href='/register') Sign Up
    .container
      .section
        // Icon Section
        .row
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              // FIRST THIRD OF THE PAGE, THE PROBLEM
              h5.center Find Your College
              p.light
                | MapOurTours provides an easy, accessible way to search for the
                | colleges you want to visit.  Simply search our map by location or college name
                | to find the college that is the perfect match for you.  From there it is easy
                | to book available campus tours.  Book more than one tour and add them to your
                | schedule to keep track of all of your college visits.
          // SECOND THIRD, THE SOLUTION
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              h5.center Why MapOurTours?
              p.light
                | MapOurTours is designed to improve the process of scheduling and
                | booking college tours by putting all of your information in one
                | place.  After signing up, a user has the ability to book any college
                | tour. 
                br
                br
                | MapOurTours saves users' information for booking a campus tour; this
                |                 way the user does not have to re-enter their information every time they want to book
                |                 a tour.
                |                 The search map makes it easy to see what colleges are near you or near the area you are
                |                 visiting.  This
                |                 feature gives users the ability to schedule tours with
                |                 colleges that they hadn’t planned on visiting prior to using our
                |                 website.  MapOurTours makes the booking process a simple, accessible, and
                |                 enjoyable experience so students can get the most out of their visits.
          // ABOUT US
